text: Mammillaria karwinskiana is a species of cacti in the subtribe Cactinae. It is native to Mexico. ==Gallery== Mammillaria karwinskiana ssp nejapensis pm 1.JPG Mammillaria karwinskiana ssp collinsii pm 1.JPG Cactus photo-Mammillaria Nejapensis.jpg Mammillaria_karwinskiana_karwinskiana_01_ies.jpg ==References== ==External links== * Mammillaria karwinskiana at Tropicos Category:Plants described in 1832 karwinskiana
